display the output on the local Virtual Machine OS(ubuntu 22.04)
-> TERMINAL OF UBUNTU

sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y  //Update system:
sudo apt install apache2 -y //Install Apache:
cd /var/www/html //Go to web root:
sudo rm index.html //(Optional) Remove default page:
sudo nano dashboard.html //Create HTML file:
(Paste your HTML, then press Ctrl+O, Enter, Ctrl+X)
sudo chmod 644 dashboard.html //Set permissions:
Go to http://localhost/dashboard.html //Open in browser:
